Subseries A: Book Proposal Materials for Webster's Dictionary Cookbook

Scope and Contents note

Series III.A contains notes and correspondence on the subject of Webster's Dictionary Cookbook, a project on which Cecile Brownstone worked with her nephew, Jonathan Ned Katz. The material spans the period of 1985-1989, and its arrangment reflects Cecile's original categorization.
